oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Canning label for Rugby Brand tomatoes, by the Rugby Canning Co.
Rugby attempted to establish a tomato canning operation in 1883, but after the cannery was constructed, colonists failed to grow enough tomatoes to keep it operational.
